Street Inn. BARBARA MARTIN PINHERO / Los Angeles Times; Photo, The J Street 
Inn, Quigley's second downtown SRO, uses balconies to break up the exterior 
walls. VINCE COMPAGNONE / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
